        "type": "p",
        "text": "In VS Code, create a new file with the <code class=\"language-malloy\" style=\"background-color: #FBFBFB\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">.</span><span style=\"color: #001080\">malloynb</span></span></code> extension:"
