      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "<a href=\"https://github.com/malloydata/malloy-samples/blob/main/faa/carrier_analysis.malloynb\">Carrier Analysis</a> - Flight carrier performance"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "<a href=\"https://github.com/malloydata/malloy-samples/blob/main/auto_recalls/README.malloynb\">Auto Recalls</a> - Example of starting with an import"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "<strong>Tip:</strong> Press <code class=\"language-malloy\" style=\"background-color: #FBFBFB\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">.</span></span></code> on any GitHub page to open it in github.dev (VS Code in the browser)."
      }
