        "type": "code",
        "text": "<pre class=\"language-malloy\" style=\"background-color: #FBFBFB\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #008000\">// Good - AI understands intent</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">measure</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #001080\">customer_lifetime_value</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> </span><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">is</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">measure</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #001080\">monthly_recurring_revenue</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> </span><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">is</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #008000\">// Bad - cryptic abbreviations</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">measure</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #001080\">clv</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> </span><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">is</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">measure</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">: </span><span style=\"color: #001080\">mrr</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> </span><span style=\"color: #AF00DB\">is</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"> ...</span></span></pre>"
